{"tid":649470,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[召飛機膠團團友]加拿大喪飛細飛機","createTime":"2018-05-01T15:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T23:35:47.000Z","uid":164871,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"744aaecfdad9e54e80cb94405d8475425b1b2d6a","tid":649470,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的﹐最近想炒老細魷魚﹐而交低辭職信後不留一點雲彩去旅行是常識吧。所以呢﹐我就想攪個飛機膠團﹐揸小型飛機圍住加拿大飛個圈（我自己係機師）。由於內容既問題﹐自問係飛機膠﹐又有時間行個圈﹐仲想去下加拿大小鎮睇下﹐咁就岩你啦！ <br />\n之前其實都勁UP過類似既計劃﹐但之前一切都留係勁UP階段﹐連PLAN都未出過。 <br />\n今次呢﹐終於有計劃啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日期︰ <br />\n<br />\n話明炒老細魷魚﹐多數係黎緊一兩個月﹐可以大家夾下。再遲可能已經有新工﹐唔係話唔走得﹐但又會再煩D﹐可以傾﹐但去唔去到隨緣啦。 <br />\n<br />\n旅程︰ <br />\n<br />\n西圈包括Albert、Saskatchewan、Manitoba﹐包括三省主要城市﹐Winnipeg、Gimli、Brandon、Regina、Calgary、Edmonton、Yellowknife、Saskatoon、Churchill。 <br />\nFlight Time 係 Skyvector 勁計就37個鐘﹐旅程約十日。咁你應該要兩星期以上既假先夠。 <br />\n<br />\n有咩做︰飛機館 X N﹐城市夜景 X N﹐飛機庫 X N﹐大量影相機會。重點大城市會留多陣。（詳細睇下面）<br />\n<br />\n團友數︰1 - 2位 <br />\n<br />\n錢︰唔包香港 &lt;-&gt; 加拿大機票。含食、住、行一位5千加幣應該得 點解咁貴？小型飛機低飛阻力大﹐油錢都貴呀。 <br />\n<br />\n====== <br />\nWest Circle: <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\nGimli <br />\nGimli Glider Museum <br />\n(1 hours flight) <br />\nBrandon <br />\nCommonwealth Air Training Plan Museum <br />\n(2 hours flight) <br />\nRegina <br />\nCity Flight <br />\n<br />\nDay 2 - 3 <br />\n( 4 hours flight) <br />\nCalgary <br />\nThe Hanger Flight Museum <br />\nThe Military Museum <br />\n<br />\nDay 4 <br />\nCalgary: Rocky Mountains <br />\n( 1+ hours flight ) <br />\nEdmonton <br />\nAlberta Aviation Museum <br />\n<br />\nDay 5 &ndash; 6 <br />\n(6+ hours flight) <br />\nYellowknife <br />\nBuffalo Airways <br />\n<br />\nDay 7 <br />\n(7+ hours flight) <br />\nSaskatoon <br />\nCity of Bridges (Air City Tour) <br />\n<br />\nDay 8 - 9 <br />\n(7 hours flight) <br />\nChurchill <br />\nMV Ithaca <br />\nChurchill Rocket Range <br />\nMiss Piggy <br />\nParks Canada Visitor Reception Centre <br />\nHudson Bay <br />\n<br />\nDay 10 <br />\n(6 hours flight) <br />\nGimli <br />\n<br />\n===== <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東圈遲下PO﹐其實我估西圈玩得成就未必會去東圈。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡︰TG︰hkpilotca"},{"pid":"ce264bcd092880be4813476b291b55ac9c9f1b53","tid":649470,"uid":154062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"PPL holder?"},{"pid":"2d6675377cd434cdf7bbb8756d71d557c73b01e8","tid":649470,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:11:56.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"681190857ccc2aec55516c4782e42b6adf3da448","tid":649470,"uid":164871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"東圈︰Gimli、Quebec、St. John、Montreal、Toronto、Winnipeg。Flight time 53 hours。相對地旅行性質比西圈高﹐加拿大重點城市都會經過。 <br />\n<br />\n錢︰8千左右 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n====Ease Circle <br />\nDay 1 <br />\nGimli <br />\nGimli Glider Museum <br />\n(6 hours flight) <br />\n<br />\nMoosenee <br />\nSouthern point of Hudson Bay <br />\n<br />\nDay 2 - 3 <br />\n(4 hours flight) <br />\nQuebec <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 <br />\n(9 hours flight) <br />\nSt. John <br />\nMost Easterly City of Canada <br />\nDay 5 <br />\n(10 hours flight) <br />\nQuebec <br />\n<br />\nDay 6 &ndash; 7 <br />\n(4 hours flight) <br />\nMontreal <br />\n<br />\nDay 8 - 9 <br />\n(3 hours flight) <br />\nToronto <br />\n<br />\nDay 10 <br />\n(9 hours flight) <br />\nThunder Bay <br />\n<br />\nDay 11 <br />\n(6 hours flight) <br />\nWinnipeg + Gimli"},{"pid":"ce6ff668e9954d8a2927b03043fb23ada7c54b42","tid":649470,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"更正︰西圈約6-7千"},{"pid":"18a747ad79a9e35edbf947f9ae282186a2d6171e","tid":649470,"uid":164871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce264bcd092880be4813476b291b55ac9c9f1b53","tid":649470,"uid":154062,"like":0,"dislike":0